---
/**
 * Accent.astro
 * ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 * Tiny wrapper for italic-serif emphasis inside a sans
 * display headline. Usage:
 *
 *   <h1>Engineering longer, <Accent>better</Accent>, sharper lives.</h1>
 *
 * Renders <span class="accent">…</span>. The `.accent`
 * utility is defined in global.css and applies the
 * --font-accent (Instrument Serif) at italic weight.
 */
---

<span class="accent"><slot /></span>
